#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:3
msgid ""
"The Carpentries supports and maintains Lesson Programs. Lesson Programs "
"are collections of lessons comprising one or more Carpentries workshops, "
"serving distinct goals and audience, and the leadership guiding their "
"development and implementation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:5
msgid ""
"From The Carpentries Bylaws:*A Lesson Program within The Carpentries "
"possesses the following characteristics:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:7
msgid ""
"Intention and purpose for lessons that align with The Carpentries mission"
" and vision"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:8
msgid ""
"Goals and objectives for lessons and/or workshops that are distinct from "
"other Lesson Programs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:9
msgid "Service to a particular audience of learners and instructors"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:10
msgid ""
"Evidence of community member commitment to Lesson Program governance (see"
" below), lesson maintenance, and curriculum development*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:12
msgid ""
"Adoption as an official The Carpentries Lesson Program is the last step "
"of Lesson Program incubation as outlined in the Lesson Program Incubation"
" Roadmap"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:14
msgid ""
"This Policy outlines the Roles and Responsibilities of the Lesson "
"Programs and The Carpentries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:16
msgid "Lesson Program Policy"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:18
msgid "Roles and Responsibilities of Lesson Programs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:20
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program maintains a Lesson Program Committee of a minimum of 3"
" members to serve as community governance body and act as a point of "
"contact with The Carpentries Executive Council and staff."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:21
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program Committee provides the Executive Council with an "
"annual report of Lesson Program operations based on a template provided "
"by The Carpentries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:22
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program follows all general policies as outlined by The "
"Carpentries, including, but not limited to, the Code of Conduct."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:23
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program workshops are conducted and administered as outlined "
"in The Carpentries handbook, including tracking activities and using at "
"least one certified instructor per workshop."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:24
msgid ""
"Assessment of Lesson Program workshops and activities are conducted "
"through, and in coordination with, The Carpentries assessment efforts."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:25
msgid ""
"Lesson Program workshops follow The Carpentries instructor training "
"procedures and guidelines as outlined in the instructor training "
"curriculum."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:26
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program has at least one articulated, established core "
"curriculum for a workshop and guidelines on what is required for it to be"
" called a Lesson Program workshop."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:27
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program maintains documentation with information about its "
"goals, workshops and curriculum."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:28
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program coordinates with The Carpentries to release and "
"publish lessons with permanent identifiers on a regular basis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:29
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program develops all content collaboratively and openly with a"
" Carpentries approved open license."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:30
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program maintains and develops lessons in accordance with "
"Carpentries guidelines as outlined in The Carpentries Curriculum "
"Development Handbook."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:31
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program uses Carpentries templates and curricular guidelines "
"for workshops and lessons."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:32
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program has a workshop fee structure and Member Organisation "
"engagement plan consistent with The Carpentries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:33
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program promotes its curriculum so that workshops are taught "
"regularly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:34
msgid ""
"The Lesson Program will follow the procedures and guidelines of The "
"Carpentries administrative and financial management structure."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:36
msgid "Roles and Responsibilities of The Carpentries"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:38
msgid ""
"The Carpentries staff and affiliates will coordinate Lesson Program "
"workshops in accordance with standard workshop coordination practices as "
"outlined in The Carpentries Handbook."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:39
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will enable the Lesson Programs to make use of all The "
"Carpentries infrastructure, including workshop coordination tools and "
"database."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:40
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will provide the Lesson Programs access to all lesson and"
" workshop templates. The Carpentries will include representatives from "
"the Lesson Program on task forces or committees tasked with updating and "
"maintaining these templates."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:41
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will support development opportunities for the Lesson "
"Program, including grants, donations and other revenue opportunities. "
"Funds brought in for Lesson Program activities will go to support that "
"work."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:42
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will include Lesson Programs in the regular lesson "
"release and publication cycle, coordinating between the Lesson Program "
"maintainers and The Carpentries staff and affiliates."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:43
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will include the Lesson Programs in assessment efforts, "
"including survey development and data analysis."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:44
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will ensure the instructor training program addresses the"
" training needs of the Lesson Program, incorporating examples and "
"exercises targeted towards the communities served by the Lesson Program."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:45
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will prepare Trainers to work with trainees from the "
"Lesson Program."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:46
msgid ""
"The Carpentries Instructor Training recruitment and retention strategies "
"will include building communities of InstructorsIinstructors in "
"communities and domains served by the Lesson Program."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:47
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will include the Lesson Program in all community efforts,"
" including but not limited to the activities of the Instructor "
"Development committee, Mentorship program and BugBBQs."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:48
msgid ""
"The Carpentries programmatic and assessment reports will include Lesson "
"Program activities. The Lesson Program will also have access to data "
"specific to its activities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:49
msgid ""
"The Carpentries Organisational Membership program will include The Lesson"
" Program."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:50
msgid ""
"The Carpentries will provide an annual financial report to the Lesson "
"Program Committee, including an assessment of the financial stability and"
" sustainability of The Carpentries."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:51
msgid ""
"The Carpentries general revenue through Memberships, workshop "
"coordination fees and general grants or donations, will support the "
"ongoing work of the Lesson Program - running workshops, diversity and "
"inclusion efforts, instructor training, lesson maintenance and community "
"engagement."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/governance/lesson-program-policy.md:52
msgid ""
"The Carpentries maintains and documents an administrative and financial "
"management structure that supports the Lesson Program."
msgstr ""

